<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h1 class="mb-3">Our Services</h1>
      <p class="lead">Discover our range of professional massage therapy services designed to meet your wellness needs.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row g-4">
    <% if (services && services.length > 0) { %>
      <% services.forEach(service => { %>
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
          <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
            <% if (service.imageUrl) { %>
              <img src="<%= service.imageUrl %>" class="card-img-top" alt="<%= service.name %>" loading="lazy">
            <% } %>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title h4"><%= service.name %></h2>
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-3">
                <span class="badge bg-primary rounded-pill"><%= service.duration %> minutes</span>
                <span class="text-primary fw-bold">$<%= service.price %></span>
              </div>
              <p class="card-text"><%= service.description %></p>
              <div class="d-grid mt-auto">
                <a href="/booking?service=<%= service.id %>" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Book This Service</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% }) %>
    <% } else { %>
      <div class="col-12 text-center">
        <div class="alert alert-info">
          <p class="mb-0">No services available at the moment. Please check back later.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% } %>
  </div>

  <div class="row my-5">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <div class="card bg-light shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body p-4">
          <h2 class="card-title h4 text-center mb-4">Massage Benefits</h2>
          <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
              <div class="text-center">
                <i class="bi bi-heart fs-1 text-primary mb-3"></i>
                <h3 class="h5">Stress Reduction</h3>
                <p>Massage therapy helps reduce stress hormones and promotes relaxation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
              <div class="text-center">
                <i class="bi bi-activity fs-1 text-primary mb-3"></i>
                <h3 class="h5">Pain Relief</h3>
                <p>Regular massages can help alleviate chronic pain and muscle tension.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
              <div class="text-center">
                <i class="bi bi-droplet fs-1 text-primary mb-3"></i>
                <h3 class="h5">Improved Circulation</h3>
                <p>Massage enhances blood flow and promotes better circulation throughout the body.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row mb-5">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body p-4">
          <h2 class="card-title h4 text-center mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq1">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqCollapse1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqCollapse1">
                  How often should I get a massage?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="faqCollapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq1" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  The frequency of massage sessions depends on your individual needs and goals. For general wellness and stress management, a monthly massage is often beneficial. For specific conditions or during periods of high stress, weekly sessions might be more appropriate. Your massage therapist can recommend a schedule that's right for you.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq2">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqCollapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqCollapse2">
                  What should I expect during my first massage?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="faqCollapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq2" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  During your first visit, you'll complete a brief health history form. Your massage therapist will discuss your goals and any areas of concern. You'll be given privacy to undress to your comfort level and lie on the massage table under a sheet or towel. The therapist will knock before re-entering. Throughout the massage, the therapist will check in about pressure and comfort. Only the area being worked on will be uncovered.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq3">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqCollapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqCollapse3">
                  Should I tip my massage therapist?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="faqCollapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq3" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Tipping is always appreciated but not required. If you choose to tip, 15-20% of the service price is customary, similar to other service industries. Some clients prefer to tip in cash even when paying for the service by card.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row mb-5">
    <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
      <h3>Ready to experience the benefits of massage therapy?</h3>
      <p class="mb-4">Book your appointment today and take the first step towards relaxation and wellness.</p>
      <a href="/booking" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Book Your Appointment</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
